OL,6,FA company in has been fined #300,000
OL,7,Fafter a father-of-two was killed by a
OL,8,Fshovel loader.
OL,10,FAnthony Bilton, from , Vale of
OL,11,FGlamorgan, died on 4 September 2019
OL,12,Fwhen he was run over from behind by a
OL,13,FVolvo shovel loader at Atlantic
OL,14,FRecycling Limited's Atlantic Ecopark
OL,15,Fsite
OL,17,FThe 59-year-old had been on his way to
OL,18,Fundertake routine maintenance tasks
OL,19,Fwhen the fatal incident happened,
OL,20,Fwhile he was walking across the wood
OL,21,Fprocessing yard.
