OL,6,FAnthony's son, Jason, said his life
OL,7,Fwas "torn to shreds" following the
OL,8,Fpassing of his dad.
OL,10,FHe said: "It took over three hours for
OL,11,Fme to be notified that my dad had been
OL,12,Fkilled in a work accident. I started
OL,13,Fto become concerned when he weren't
OL,14,Fhome from work at his usual time and
OL,15,Ffailed to answer the phone.
