OL,6,F"I remember thinking about popping by
OL,7,Fhis workplace to see him whilst on my
OL,8,Fjourney home from Telford, where I'd
OL,9,Fbeen for the past few days, but
OL,10,Fdecided against it as I was exhausted
OL,11,Ffrom traveling.
OL,13,F"Had I gone to see him, I would've
OL,14,Farrived at Atlantic Recycling between
OL,15,F3:30-4pm, he was killed around 4:10pm.
OL,16,FEvery day I deal with thoughts that:
OL,17,F'If only I'd stopped to see him, he
OL,18,Fcould still be alive today.'"
