OL,6,FJason Bilton said he suffered anxiety
OL,7,Fand depression, which left him unable
OL,8,Fto work.
OL,10,FHe faced financial issues, as he had
OL,11,Flived with Mr Bilton and they had paid
OL,12,Fhalf of household bills each.
OL,14,FHe initially returned to work for fear
OL,15,Fof debt building up, and becoming
OL,16,Fhomeless.
OL,18,FHe expressed anger about proceedings
OL,19,Fbeing dragged out for three years,
OL,20,Fwhich left him unable to move on from
OL,21,Fhis father's death.
