OL,6,FHe added, "There will never be real
OL,7,Fclosure for my dad's death as it
OL,8,Fshould never have happened, not the
OL,9,Fway it did. My life was torn to shreds
OL,10,Fwithin a few hours and to this day I'm
OL,11,Fstill dealing with the consequences
OL,12,Fand emotional impact."
OL,14,FAtlantic Recycling Limited, of Newton
OL,15,FRoad, Rumney, Cardiff, pleaded guilty
OL,16,Fto breaching Section 2(1) of the
OL,17,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,18,F1974. The company was fined #300,000
OL,19,Fand ordered to pay #29,917.47 in costs
OL,20,Fat on 28 February 2024.
